Privacy Policy

Radha Jap Counter app respects your privacy. This privacy policy explains how we handle your information when you use our app.


Information We Collect

We do not collect, store, or share any personal information from users.
The app operates entirely on your device and does not require user registration or login.


Data Storage

All data including jap counts, settings, and preferences are stored locally on your device only.
We do not have access to this data and it is never uploaded to our servers.


Permissions

The app may request audio permissions to play background music and bhajans.
These permissions are used solely for app functionality and not for collecting data.

